OL,5, A tenant has told of the moment he was 
OL,6, confronted by a man he believed to be  
OL,7, his landlord during a rent row.        
OL,9,FJason Chen took a secret video         
OL,10,Frecording of the incident where the man
OL,11,Fis seen waving a stool during the      
OL,12,Fdispute over Mr Chen's Edinburgh flat  
OL,13,Fgoing without hot water for 28 days.   
OL,15,FMr Chen believes the man in the video  
OL,16,Fis flat owner and controversial        
OL,17,Fbusinessman Mark Fortune.              
OL,19,FMr Fortune denied this and said he was 
OL,20,Fat the dentist in France at the time.  
